@tqchen The simulation code in Intel HLS current only works in simulation mode. I have manually migrated the HLS code into Chisel3, and the `metal_tests` of ALU functions (including scalar-vector and vector-vector operations) are successful on DE10-Nano hardware.
@tmoreau89 @nhynes @vegaluisjose Please take a review.
If there is no other issue, I would continue to add the GEMM into current implement in Chisel.
